Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shop Closed Today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just standin' there for? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, how about openin' the door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:00.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.73,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ritsuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:15.95,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.67,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I love the cakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. This is Brother Jun's family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:27.25,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.72,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, why don't you come over \Nto my place to watch them practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.63,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... She hates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.81,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What is that, avant-garde?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Richie. Get your head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,How we gonna have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, Yurika-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:03:02.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, didn't your dad tell you that \Noutsiders aren't allowed down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:07.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san is our friend, so \NI'm sure Dad wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yurika-san, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.50,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.75,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to get a little fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.58,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Richie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro's sister... Sachiko-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.74,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All my friends are \Noff at cram school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:53.64,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.79,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.59,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not playing? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:07.10,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's a relic, so \Nsometimes it gets ornery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.78,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, you have \Nto work a little magic on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:18.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Brother Jun. How'd that get it to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:20.83,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:25.15,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, is this the Children's \NTelephone Counseling Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:33.88,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,See, there's this boy, Hashiguchi-kun, \Nwho's always mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.13,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He hides my slippers, pulls my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.53,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:48.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe that Hashiguchi-kun \Nactually likes you, Sachiko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is he wants to be friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but doesn't know how to express his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so he acts out like that without \Nreally thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.44,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:07.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I made the girl \Nthat I really like cry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but even if I do, I don't \Nthink she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:17.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.78,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I can't stay mad at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.90,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:47.16,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, I've been \Ngoing to the shop for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it was your family's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.29,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayuri
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.29,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The coincidences keep on coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.29,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even the name is similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:09.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's someone that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right now... he's the only \None I can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered by the way you \Nfeel about me, Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.44,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You seem kinda troubled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat this an' cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I said something terrible to Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:54.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san might not come back here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.71,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:06.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...know who Ri'ko li...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.95,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.06,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.73,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,School starts again today...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to talk about \Nromantic stuff here in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come over for \Npractice during winter vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:45.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... The teacher told \Nme to give this to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's finally come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but everything seems so bleak right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't bring myself \Nto talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...! What are you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, get a jacket on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko is lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:47.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, all you gotta \Ndo is stop by the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.09,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.25,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a loud noise \Ncoming from here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:10.73,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Actually, I wanted \Nto give you this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.41,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Shizu-san, our \Nold housekeeper, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:17.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san? Oh, that takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.21,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.92,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We've had our problems over the years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.67,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,...but it seems Shizu-san happened \Nto run into your mother in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:35.43,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She got your mother's address and \Ninsisted I pass it on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.83,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We split up when you were still little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so you might not remember \Nyour mom very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:48.19,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd like to go see her, you \Ncould, maybe on your next break...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.45,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden and \Nmay leave you at a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.79,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but whether you go or not \Nis totally up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.81,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let you get back to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie. You can bring her some \Nsweet rice treats as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:10.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're not goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm just not up to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.01,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You know where she is {\i1}now{\i0},\N and if you lose this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,you'll regret it for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.18,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.74,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.28,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, you're hiding \Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, not especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.84,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Blue trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.89,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,"Blue trains" basically refers to \Nlimited express trains from Asakaze on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.47,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,that have dedicated blue sleeper cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.93,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the design of the \Nfront and back car are different
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.13,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,because they have to switch \Noff being the lead car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is \Nmy first time traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like a trip to help \Nme get over my heartache?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're late, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, it's a good thing I \Nasked Maruo to get me a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:43.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like takin' a trip to \NTokyo too, so I'm taggin' along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:53.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I only went on this trip so I could be \Nalone and think things over quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Man, travel an' frozen tangerines \Ngo together like bread an' butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.43,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I do have one more tangerine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,They taste better before they thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Maruo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how can you afford this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I had money saved up \Nfrom my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And then I sold some old records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have nearly enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:25.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I can make it to Brother \NJun's place, I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What a thoughtless fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is yours, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko said the food in the dining \Ncar is probably expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so she made these for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:46.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't you gonna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She's been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with all these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a festival? Or a New Year's sale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Station is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go sightseeing around Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see what your mom's \Nlike, so I'm comin' with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.46,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:39.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck?! This is some workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, maybe I got the address wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.79,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go in an' ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind about meeting her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?! \NYou've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if I don't see her... \NEven if I did, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She says it's your mom's day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Said she'd meet you here tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll come back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:23.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I say we relax a \Nbit at Brother Jun's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:32.60,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two have business \Nwith Katsuragi Junichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:33.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.95,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no point in waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.34,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,He's been missing since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Missing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:46.29,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Rumor has it he got in bad with \Nsome faction and now he's in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:50.74,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's possible he's just \Nshacking up with some girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.66,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.66,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's popular with college girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that doesn't surprise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, not surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:04.35,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Have you two come all the way from Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:12.69,Main Dialog,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's make our guests from \Nfaraway Kyushu feel welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.52,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,With shochu and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.25,Main Dialog,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.93,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.86,Main Dialog,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:29.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You wouldn't \Nbelieve how stupid this guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's no end of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:36.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with him, his \Nstupidity rubs off on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.29,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you. You're lucky \Nto have such a good buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Buddy? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:47.30,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it's the most! Pretty rare \Nto have a friend you can get goofy with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:49.77,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.91,Main Dialog,Okada,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike love affairs, friendship is for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.80,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.91,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, that is you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:25.34,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What are you standing \Naround like a scarecrow for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.75,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.76,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Hurry up and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten fancy \Ncurry like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.05,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, don't be shy. Just eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:43.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.31,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I like the way you shovel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.74,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a thing for men \Nwith a hearty appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:54.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't at all like I imagined her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru and Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:04.39,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?! Mother and \Nson perfectly in unison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... He has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.79,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you friends from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Or more like, we play music together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's a drummer and I play the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.36,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.96,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru, you used to love it \Nwhen your dad played the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.19,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He would play and I'd sing along...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.95,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,And then, even if you were crying, \Nyou'd always stop and listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:35.96,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a happy memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I don't remember at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:44.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, Dad never likes \Nto talk about the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.50,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.84,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want to talk about \Na washout of a mother like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rain has stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm gonna take a little \Nstroll around Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.27,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think he wanted to give us some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:05.69,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.22,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's this curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.96,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's spicier than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.46,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:31.58,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.65,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a girl that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:39.02,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Did it not work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:42.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom... I'd rather not talk \Nabout that right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.42,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What, I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:50.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just the idea of \Nthe baby boy in my memory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:54.70,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,who'd say "Mama" and make gurgling \Nnoises... having a broken heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.07,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the heyday of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.25,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A broken heart! Not bad, not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:09.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm lovelorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The more I laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,the more whatever had been building up \Ninside me disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My mind emptied out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:29.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.22,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a jazz record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The song called "Lullaby of Birdland".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen and then try singing along to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back to visit you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...so until then, I'd like \Nyou to practice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.81,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But this is in English, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:50.00,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the language at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. Just imitate what you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jazz is best when sung by \Na woman with a husky voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back for sure, \Nso practice, Mom, practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.76,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.74,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:14.27,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I thought... I'd probably \Nnever see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.68,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my mom leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:40.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those words that I couldn't ask flew \Naway somewhere with this scenery...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:45.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's mouth formed the words, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:51.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I shook my head, but I'm not sure she saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That was heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Where were ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Ri-chan.
